<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دراهم أو أربعة <span class="c2">(دراهم)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
